{"word":"鞍","detail":[{"title":"基本字义解释","content":[[{"type":"text","content":"● "},{"type":"strong","content":"鞍"},{"type":"span","content":"ānㄢˉ","class":["pinyin"]}],[{"type":"text","content":"◎ 套在骡马背上便于骑坐的东西：马"},{"type":"span","content":"鞍","class":["fontred"]},{"type":"text","content":"。"},{"type":"span","content":"鞍","class":["fontred"]},{"type":"text","content":"鞒。"},{"type":"span","content":"鞍","class":["fontred"]},{"type":"text","content":"韂（"},{"type":"span","content":"chàn","class":["pinyin"]},{"type":"text","content":"）（马鞍和垫在马鞍下面的东西。亦称“鞍鞯”）。"}]]},{"title":"英文翻译","content":[[{"type":"text","content":"saddle; any saddle-shaped object"}]]},{"title":"详细字义解释","content":[[{"type":"text","content":"◎ "},{"type":"strong","content":"鞍"},{"type":"text","content":" "},{"type":"span","content":"ān","class":["pinyin"]},{"type":"text","content":" "},{"type":"img","content":"","class":["sound"]},{"type":"text","content":" "}],[{"type":"span","content":"〈名词〉","class":["parts"]}],[{"type":"text","content":"(1) (形声。从革,安声。本义:马鞍)同本义"},{"type":"br","content":""},{"type":"text","content":"鞌,鞁具也。——《说文》"},{"type":"br","content":""},{"type":"text","content":"令皆下马解鞍。——《汉书·李广传》"},{"type":"br","content":""},{"type":"text","content":"投鞌高如城者数所。——《汉书·韩安国传》"},{"type":"br","content":""},{"type":"text","content":"汉王下马踞鞍而问。——《史记·留侯世家》。"}],[{"type":"text","content":"(2) 又如:鞍桥(指马鞍。因马鞍的形状像桥而得名);鞍辔(骑马的用具。鞍为坐具,辔为控马的缰束)"}]]},{"title":"常用词组","content":[[{"type":"text","content":"◎  "},{"type":"strong","content":"鞍马"},{"type":"text","content":" "},{"type":"span","content":"ānmǎ","class":["cpinyin"]}],[{"type":"text","content":"(1)泛指马和马具"},{"type":"br","content":""},{"type":"text","content":"愿为市鞍马,从此替爷征。——《木兰诗》"},{"type":"br","content":""},{"type":"text","content":"(2)指人骑的马"},{"type":"br","content":""},{"type":"text","content":"而操舍鞍马,仗舟楫,与吴越争衡。——司马光《资治通鉴》"},{"type":"br","content":""},{"type":"text","content":"(3)骑马的人"},{"type":"br","content":""},{"type":"text","content":"门前冷落鞍马稀。——白居易《琵琶行》"},{"type":"br","content":""},{"type":"text","content":"(4)一种体育器材,形状略像马,背部有两个半圆环,可以调整高度,用来做体操"}],[{"type":"text","content":"◎  "},{"type":"strong","content":"鞍马劳顿，鞍马劳倦，鞍马劳神"},{"type":"text","content":" "},{"type":"span","content":"ānmǎ-láodùn,ānmǎ-láojuàn,ānmǎ-láoshén","class":["cpinyin"]}],[{"type":"text","content":"长途策马跋涉,劳累疲困"}],[{"type":"text","content":"◎  "},{"type":"strong","content":"鞍子"},{"type":"text","content":" "},{"type":"span","content":"ānzi","class":["cpinyin"]}],[{"type":"text","content":"放在牲畜(如马、骡)背上以便人乘坐或驮运物品的器具,用皮革包木制成"}]]},{"title":"康熙字典","content":[[{"type":"text","content":"【戌集中】【革字部】鞍 ·康熙筆画：15　·部外筆画：6 "}],[{"type":"text","content":"【韻會】同鞌。【前漢·李廣傳】令皆下馬解鞍。"}]]},{"title":"字源演变","content":[]},{"title":"同音字","content":[]}],"type":"通用字、次常用字","pinyin":["ān"],"radical":"革","stroke":"六画","total_stroke":"十五画","stroke_order":"一丨丨一丨フ一一丨丶丶フフノ一","input_method":{"bopomofo":"TJJV","number":"43544","unicode":"U+978D","wubi":"AFPV"}}